id: pm-doxj
title: pm-cli post-v0.1 roadmap & living backlog
description: "Forward-looking roadmap milestone anchoring the open, living backlog for pm-cli beyond v0.1. Complements (does not duplicate) the closed PRD delivery milestones."
type: Milestone
status: open
priority: 0
tags[6]: backlog,context-management,living-map,pm-cli,post-v0.1,roadmap
created_at: "2026-05-31T19:41:50.865Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-09T10:35:50.550Z"
author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 60
acceptance_criteria: Living backlog reflects the entire ecosystem; every capability epic has defined acceptance and active children; periodic review passes keep zero orphan open items and zero untracked work streams.
goal: project management = context management
objective: "Deliver a universal, fully-customizable PM tool whose baseline primitives (via the pm SDK) adapt to any project"
value: A discoverable forward backlog turns the tracker from a completed-work log into a living context map for humans and agents
why_now: Tracker had 902 items but zero open/forward work; pm context returned empty. This milestone seeds the forward layer.
risk: low
confidence: high
